Package pl.polsl.lab.model

Class Posts

java.lang.Object
pl.polsl.lab.model.Posts
public class Posts extends Object
Manages a list of posts, allowing for adding new posts, getting a list of posts, and setting the list of posts.
Author:
Jakub Janszak
